1121
00:55:15,931 --> 00:55:18,398
That paternity wrap, a couple years ago.

1122
00:55:18,500 --> 00:55:19,232
Morty!

1123
00:55:19,334 --> 00:55:20,100
Did you shtup her?

1124
00:55:20,202 --> 00:55:21,635
Morty, shut up!

1125
00:55:21,737 --> 00:55:23,303
Did you go all the way?

1126
00:55:23,405 --> 00:55:24,538
- What?
- Morty!

1127
00:55:24,640 --> 00:55:26,206
- Uncle Morty, you are...
- What?

