00:55:26,308 --> 00:55:26,907
My god.

1129
00:55:27,009 --> 00:55:28,041
It's all right.

1130
00:55:28,143 --> 00:55:28,809
It's all right.

1131
00:55:28,911 --> 00:55:30,777
All right... It's all right.

1132
00:55:30,879 --> 00:55:34,614
Morty, I hope this doesn't
lessen your opinion of me,

1133
00:55:34,716 --> 00:55:37,584
but the answer is no.

1134
00:55:37,686 --> 00:55:42,923
You see, people like me, we're targets.

1135
00:55:43,025 --> 00:55:44,558
I'm blamed for a lot of things I had

1136
00:55:44,660 --> 00:55:46,093
absolutely nothing to do with.

1137
00:55:46,195 --> 00:55:49,729
On the other hand, because of who I am,

1138
00:55:49,832 --> 00:55:51,698
I get away with murder in other areas.

1139
00:55:51,800 --> 00:55:54,734
I suppose it all balances out in the end.

1140
00:55:54,837 --> 00:55:56,103
Does it really, Swanee?

1141
00:55:56,205 --> 00:56:00,607
Ma, he's an actor, not a river.

1142
00:56:00,709 --> 00:56:05,912
Swanee, can I talk frank to you?

1143
00:56:06,014 --> 00:56:07,014
Certainly, Belle.

1144
00:56:11,086 --> 00:56:13,553
Take a good look here.

1145
00:56:13,655 --> 00:56:18,024
This this... this is good.

1146
00:56:18,127 --> 00:56:20,961
Sitting around with people you love.

1147
00:56:21,063 --> 00:56:24,264
Some you just like, others,
maybe you could live without,

1148
00:56:24,366 --> 00:56:25,366
excuse me.

1149
00:56:27,069 --> 00:56:31,738
Sharing stories, sharing warm...

1150
00:56:31,840 --> 00:56:34,007
This is real life, Alan.

1151
00:56:34,109 --> 00:56:36,076
