A home and a family and children?

1153
00:56:43,652 --> 00:56:46,253
Hey, who knows?

1154
00:56:46,355 --> 00:56:48,622
Unfortunately, Belle,
that part of my life

1155
00:56:48,724 --> 00:56:50,557
hasn't worked out too well.

1156
00:56:50,659 --> 00:56:54,861
Though I did produce a
perfectly glorious little child.

1157
00:56:54,963 --> 00:56:56,997
Her name is Tess.

1158
00:56:57,099 --> 00:57:02,669
See, you're a daddy,
and this I didn't even know.

1159
00:57:02,771 --> 00:57:03,970
So where is she?

1160
00:57:04,072 --> 00:57:07,107
She lives with her mother in Connecticut.

1161
00:57:07,209 --> 00:57:09,042
